readme:
Service Usage

This service is used to retrieve miscellaneous details (correspondence, group leader, tour details etc) which are associated with a parent group application (eg. ADS600 cohort).

Service Behaviour

The consumer supplies a business service identifier to the provider. If no group can be found using that identifier, the ESB will return an enterprise informational error message ENTR00016.

Transformation

Transformation exists on the ESB between enterprise and ICSE provider messages.
